commit dff98dfe900d4ae8114d3130e87877e00b980f21
Author: Marko Lindqvist <cazfi74@gmail.com>
Date:   Sun Apr 24 07:51:20 2022 +0300

    Client: Consider dev format scenarios incompatible with stable ones

