commit f11da603b65474bc55741f11f70ee2b50a380687
Author: Marko Lindqvist <cazfi74@gmail.com>
Date:   Fri Apr 16 03:07:44 2021 +0300

    Drop unused 'capital' field from PACKET_EDIT_PLAYER

