commit 0fd5f1851c28dd1570b5ff3901e5cb6aca7d4467
Author: Marko Lindqvist <cazfi74@gmail.com>
Date:   Sun May 10 10:40:11 2020 +0300

    Granularity: Add Irrigation extra

