commit 0e7791b0a7f3cbbec5936fae0804e7aa038437b2
Author: Sveinung Kvilhaugsvik <sveinung84@users.sourceforge.net>
Date:   Tue Feb 25 13:40:29 2020 +0100

    Suitcase Nuke: explain why no actprob.

