commit 4b29d6320d8f12337a2f25dc0a99eb6b79e6d4ef
Author: Hilde Bye <lagnason@hotmail.com>
Date:   Tue Dec 17 18:55:59 2019 +0100

    Actprob for transport (un/)load actions.

