r35369 | sveinung | 2017-05-02 13:47:39 +0100 (Tue, 02 May 2017) | 14 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/ai/default/aicity.c
   M /trunk/ai/default/aidata.c
   M /trunk/ai/default/aidiplomat.c
   M /trunk/client/gui-gtk-3.0/action_dialog.c
